            <title>华为撞 Apple 于同一日举行发布会，余承东：将发布华为巅峰之作</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-29</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 08:03:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[余承东]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[折叠式萤幕]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260055</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 刚宣布将于香港时间 9 月 10 日凌晨 1 时举行秋季发布会，而华为亦紧随其后宣布于 9 月 10 日举行发布会，两大发布会将于同日举行。</p><p>华为终端今（2 日）宣布，华为见非凡品牌盛典及鸿蒙智行新品发布会将于 9 月 10 日 14 时 30 分举行。华为董事余承东表示，届时将带来华为最具引领性、创新性、颠覆性的产品。他又指经过 5 年的坚持及投入，华为将意想不到的划时代产品由科幻变成现实，称大家可期待即将发布的华为巅峰之作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9-430x580.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9-430x580.jpg 430w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_ebd04964f7804635b9.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 430px" /></a></p><p>早前余承东曾在科技公司与辉同行的直播中透露，下代华为折叠式萤幕经过 5 年研发后即将面世，指这款折叠式萤幕别人想得到但做不出来。</p><p>根据网上流传的相片可见，余承东曾在一部三折叠式萤幕的新装置使用微信，左边萤幕为讯息列表，而右边则是对话框。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_e5dc36e698984eb3a0.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3-552x580.jpg" alt="" width="552" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3-552x580.jpg 552w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/s_5b1710a57fff4c55b3.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 552px" /></a></p><p>图片来源：快科技</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1000/1000757.htm">快科技</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/01/huawei-harmony-os-next-beta/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多款手机平板合资格，华为 HarmonyOS NEXT 开放大范围测试</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/huawei-watch-d2-blood-pressure-sept/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 Watch D2 传 9 月发表，将提供血压计、心电图功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/huawei-matepad-air-launch-china/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">纤薄全金属机身配大容量电池，华为 MatePad Air (2024) 中国发表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/02/huawei-29/mobile-phone/">华为撞 Apple 于同一日举行发布会，余承东：将发布华为巅峰之作</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
